#. type: Plain text
msgid "For B<munlockall>():"
msgstr "Für B<munlockall>():"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"(Linux 2.6.8 and earlier) The caller was not privileged (B<CAP_IPC_LOCK>)."
msgstr ""
"(Linux 2.6.8 und früher) Der Aufrufende war nicht privilegiert "
"(B<CAP_IPC_LOCK>)."

